# Getting Started with Vite + React

This frontend was generated by BESSER and is powered by Vite.

## Available Scripts

In the project directory, you can run:

### `npm start`

Runs the app in development mode.  
Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000) to view it in the browser.

### `npm run build`

Builds the app for production to the `build` folder.

### `npm run preview`

Serves the production build locally for a quick smoke test.

## Environment Variables

Use a `.env` file at the project root to configure backend URLs:

```
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000
VITE_AGENT_URL=ws://localhost:8765
```
